Mukherjee Says Uncertainty in Global Oil Prices `Serious Issue' for India

-- B y   T u s h a r   D h a r a
-- 
2011-03-02T10:32:21Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-02/mukherjee-says-uncertainty-in-global-oil-prices-serious-issue-for-india.html
Indian Finance Minister Pranab
Mukherjee said uncertainty in global oil prices is a “serious
issue.”   The government needs to control spending to cut the budget
deficit, Mukherjee said in an interview with Bloomberg UTV
television channel in  New Delhi  today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
